name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement
description: The SVGFEDisplacementMapElement interface corresponds to the <feDisplacementMap> element.

members.name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.in1
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.in2
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in2 attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.scale
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the scale attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.xChannelSelector
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the xChannelSelect attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_CHANNEL_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.yChannelSelector
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the yChannelSelect attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_CHANNEL_* constants defined on this interface.
